data.description: Updated beautifully landscaped tri-level home with basement. Sitting on half acre with amazing views of Owyhee Mountain range and stunning sunsets. Laminate wood flooring throughout. New furnace 2014, vinyl windows 2017, AC 2019, roof 2020, water heater 2022. Huge 17x24 family room with fireplace and half bath on lower level is perfect for all your family activities. Upstairs are 3 bedrooms 2 full baths. Basement has 2 flex rooms for bedrooms, office or hobby rooms, and 2 room size storage areas. Must see if you need space. NO HOA or CCRs. Very Large Paved area for all your toy storage and with a B-Ball Hoop. Smart gas thermostat set Fireplace in 2014. Fruit Trees and Large Garden Area.
